{
  "doc_id": "6626",
  "text": "The chromatograms were converted to FASTA format using FinchTV chromatogram viewer software. The DNA sequences in ABI file were manually edited using BioEdit v.7.0.5. Results of sequence editing were analyzed using BLAST (Basic Local Alignment Search Tool) NCBI to indicate the homology from closest species. Phylogenetic tree was constructed using maximum likelihood method, calculation using Bootstrap with 1000 times of repetition in MEGA (Molecular Evolutionary Genetic Analysis) software program v.10.0. [CITATION_1] . COI gene sequence of five coccinellid beetle (Coccinella transversalis) was also collected from National Centre for Biotechnology Information (NCBI) to compare with the research sample for their phylogenetic analysis.",
